  comm "swapper/0", pid 1, jiffies 4294892465 (age 84.616s)
  hex dump (first 32 bytes):
    40 00 56 01 08 00 ff ff 40 00 56 01 08 00 ff ff  @.V.....@.V.....
    b8 52 77 7f 08 00 ff ff 00 3c 4c 00 08 00 ff ff  .Rw......<L.....
  backtrace:
